      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and a desirable 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver\u2019s example benefits from critical preventative maintenance, including professional rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and M-spec dampers, while the factory limited-slip differential ensures optimal power delivery out of corners. The individual throttle bodies provide the signature induction note and immediate throttle modulation enthusiasts crave. Well-maintained and sorted for spirited use, this M3 balances authentic performance with daily usability.",
